title: Ryan Adams -  Live Acoustic Concert - 2002-03-08 - Seattle, WA
description:
Brilliant audience recording of an solo acoustic concert of Ryan Adams. I added the soundboard recording of Prison Letter from this concert as the last song, since it  is just awefully beautiful and was included when I found it. Bitrate: 128 kB/s


Ryan Adams
Century Ballroom
Seattle, WA
2002-03-08
